    "When asked how it can be useful for psychotherapy, it offers the following four aspects: 1) It can assist in screening and diagnosis, 2) provide information, reminders, and guidance to patients during treatment, 3) provide emotional support to patients through listening and empathy, and 4) assist with skills training (ChatGPT, personal conversation on April 14, 2023).",
